{"tid":1850771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我老豆死都唔肯帶口罩","createTime":"2020-01-29T16:53:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T04:07:00.000Z","uid":258112,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"46616fa77a1b3e1add4dc3dcd82572680d4f8126","tid":1850771,"uid":258112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:53:56.000Z","msg":"佢話佢翻工有自己車<br />\n又唔會去人多嘅地方<br />\n而且其他人都帶曬口罩<br />\n有病嘅人都帶埋<br />\n調翻轉諗就係佢都唔洗防嗰啲人<br />\n又屌9我點解落個樓下商場都要帶口罩<br />\n咁就嘥咗幾蚊<br />\n我聽完之後真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母你要死都唔緊要<br />\n咪撚拉埋我落水啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有啲咩事 實傳到俾我哋<br />\n我又無理由為咗防佢係屋企24小時帶口罩<br />\n轉頭又話9我<br />\n<br />\n真係<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0a3eecd52bd197ae5a6995352e0667b21a8d0d2","tid":1850771,"uid":258731,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:54:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/308/5d9705d903228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F308%2F5d9705d903228.jpg&h=786cb045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港共正利用武漢肺炎進行第9步：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">種族清洗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n透過邊境不設防<br />\n高調宣揚非本地人士免費優先治療武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蓄意引導大量染病支那人來港<br />\n摧毀香港已經長期超負荷的醫療系統，令香港人大規模感染<br />\n而無法隔離或治理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n中共打算將香港將變成武漢，市民無法睇醫生，橫屍街頭<br />\n意圖對香港人進行大屠殺</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣東建國 香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廣東建國 香港獨立 港中區隔"},{"pid":"907e1cec7884c49ec33b34d2f7baafab68ffee43","tid":1850771,"uid":146621,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:56:20.000Z","msg":"得罪講句<br />\n廢老唔見棺材唔流眼淚"},{"pid":"984a9320128d0df44a85ef4698ea6d7854b8d71b","tid":1850771,"uid":201414,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:56:32.000Z","msg":"幫佢買定份保險 受益人就<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a6cd9d72301bccb00661cbda2bcab7613546b54","tid":1850771,"uid":258112,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"907e1cec7884c49ec33b34d2f7baafab68ffee43","tid":1850771,"uid":146621,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:56:20.000Z","msg":"得罪講句<br />\n廢老唔見棺材唔流眼淚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:57:59.000Z","msg":"仆街 佢入棺材都唔緊要<br />\n咪搞著我啊大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3270b15fb592e30ffcf59c1d47860abd58091e0","tid":1850771,"uid":283712,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:06:33.000Z","msg":"通常啲老豆都以為自己好撚勁唔會中，啲老母意識好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7fcacd255bd0c186a4a5ec636cd91a0f1cacccb","tid":1850771,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:07:37.000Z","msg":"死都唔戴&hellip;結果咪係死"},{"pid":"2ae7b539a38d8d4eae32ab7aba9e702d1a5e4843","tid":1850771,"uid":21761,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:12:44.000Z","msg":"I know that feel...<br />\n仲要廁所板又唔蓋好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想搬出去避下先"},{"pid":"fdcb69716a0dfa7932c4e11e3563bd7bf8aa98e1","tid":1850771,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor